            </rs> the property of persons unknown, <rs id="t17810912-14-cd70" type="crimeDate">July the 17th</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810912-14-off69 t17810912-14-cd70"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17810912-14-person161">
                  CHARLES
                   WOOD
               <interp inst="t17810912-14-person161" type="surname" value="WOOD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17810912-14-person161" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
