            .)</p>
               <p>(The constable produced the sugar, and it was deposed to be the same found in the possession of the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178109120012"></xptr>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I am innocent. The first witness was a custom-house officer, and has been dismissed. I think his oath should not stand.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17810912-14-verdict72" type="verdictDescription">
